### Axioms ###
:GrapeVariety owl:equivalentClass [ owl:intersectionOf ( :usedToProduce min 1 Wine ) ] .

:Wine owl:equivalentClass [ owl:intersectionOf ( :hasVintage min 1 Vintage ) ] .

:Wine rdfs:subClassOf [ owl:onProperty :hasRating owl:someValuesFrom :Rating ] .